Dying alone
[[Image:Gayalone.JPG|thumb|Gay, elderly and alone. (In [[New York]].)]]
[[Image:Azn mans pasttime.jpg|thumb|This [[azn|Azn]] will die alone.]]
[[Image:Ufukmee.jpg|thumb|This is [[you]].]]
The journey of '''dying alone''' is not unlike the Noble Eight-Fold Path of [[Buddhism]]. One must discipline the body and mind in preparation for alienating everyone who has ever loved or cared for you (if there ever was [[family|anyone]]). The first step in this journey is often a self diagnosis of [[aspie|Assperger's]] or [[Antisocial Personality Disorder]] (sociopath). Dying alone is an endeavor which takes a lifetime of [[drugs|dedication]].



== Dying Alone Checklist ==

[[Image:wealldiealone01.jpg|thumb|OSHA-required warning sign reveals ugly truth.]]

*You're black person.
*You [[hate]] your family and they don't understand why. You pretty much deserve to die alone because of this you selfish bastard.
*<s>You [[hate]] all your ex-girlfriends/boyfriends even though they want to "like" you.</s> [[lol]] like [[you]]'ve ever had one.
*You [[hate|have no relationship with]] your neighbors.([http://theync.com/media.php?name=14419-deranged-girl-kills-herself-in-bathtub....found-days-later-decaying who will only notice/report you because of the stench of decaying flesh]).
*You [[Bill Hicks|despise humanity]] and prefer the company of [[you|yourself]], [[cat|cats]] and [[IRC|'people']] you have never met and probably never will.
*[[unemployed|You don't have a job.]] --> Ergo you don't have much money in the bank (less than zero). You don't have a car. You have little content in your wallet (three worn receipts from [[McDonald's]]). When/if you wear pants, they're jizz and urine-stained [[Steve Irwin|khakis]]. You're the all-singing ([[WHEN I WAS]]), all-dancing ([[DDR]]) [[crap]] of the world and it's your duty to refuse to participate in the [[IRL|status quo]]. 
*Every Friday night, you dress in Vietnam War era camo, load your guns, take [[heroin|Morphine]], drink Thai whiskey, and watch ''Apocalypse Now Redux'' on DVD at full volume in the dark.
*You maxed out all your credit cards on purely selfish pursuits like [[p0rn]], [[Farmville]] coins, [[Runescape]], [[McDonalds|fast]] [[KFC|food]] and whiskey. Why bother wasting other people's money on charity when you can spend it all on yourself?

The only way to prevent this is to reverse everything said above.

